Package odase.wf Description

Interface to access some workflow evaluation engine equivalent to workflow.m. Through the implementation of odase.wf.IWorkflow and odase.wf.IWorkflowExtended, the workflow can be accessed via these interfaces, or through the concrete classes Workflow and odase.wf.WorkflowExtended which provide access to a more object oriented workflow interface, with classes such as odase.wf.CheckedOutTask following the task life-cycle.
